  "frontCover": "Front cover of a greeting card with a 9:16 aspect ratio, featuring a \"thinking-of-you\" greeting. The artwork is in a stylized cartoon style with flat 2D design, using a vibrant and slightly muted color palette dominated by teal blue for the background, cream for a sign/easel, and a deep blue suit with an orange tie. The main subject is a charming, round pug character wearing a smart blue suit, a crisp white shirt, and a bright orange tie. The pug has a slightly grumpy, yet endearing expression with exaggeratedly furrowed brows and large, soulful dark eyes. It stands upright, holding two small brown briefcases, one in each paw. To the right of the pug, a cream-colored sign or easel displays bold, orange text that reads \"PUG-tential UNLIMITED, INC.\", with two thin yellow lines underlining \"UNLIMITED\". The main greeting \"Thinking of You, Future Investor...\" is prominently displayed in large, off-white, sans-serif, slightly playful block letters on the left side of the teal background, positioned safely away from the edges. The overall mood is humorous and business-oriented with a whimsical, adorable twist due to the pug character.",
