  "rightInterior": "Right interior page of a greeting card with a 9:16 aspect ratio, continuing the visual story with the same stylized cartoon art style, color palette, and flat 2D design. The core of this page is the message, presented in a beautiful, clear, handwritten cursive script, as if written with an elegant pen. The script is legible, flowing, and warm, conveying genuine affection. The message reads: \"We loooove you please invest in our company \". This handwritten text is artfully integrated with decorative elements that are both innovative and complementary to the theme, avoiding clichÃ©s. These decorative elements might include stylized, abstract representations of growing business charts, coin stacks, or playful piggy banks, rendered in the card's established color palette (teal, cream, blues, oranges). The pug character is not present on this page, allowing the message and its artistic framing to be the central focus, creating the emotional climax of the card's visual narrative. The overall mood is humorous, affectionate, and a bit cheeky, perfectly encapsulating the \"Kids\" sending the card."
